msgctxt "mn128:23.5"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, anuruddhā, puriso vaṭṭakaṃ sithilaṃ gaṇheyya, so tassa hatthato "
"uppateyya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn128:23.6"
msgid ""
"evameva kho me, anuruddhā, atilīnavīriyaṃ udapādi, atilīnavīriyādhikaraṇañca "
"pana me samādhi cavi."
