msgid ""
"‘atinijjhāyitattaṃ kho me rūpānaṃ udapādi, atinijjhāyitattādhikaraṇañca pana "
"me rūpānaṃ samādhi cavi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn128:26.7"
msgid "Samādhimhi cute obhāso antaradhāyati dassanañca rūpānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn128:26.8"
msgid ""
"Sohaṃ tathā karissāmi yathā me puna na vicikicchā uppajjissati, na "
"amanasikāro, na thinamiddhaṃ, na chambhitattaṃ, na uppilaṃ, na duṭṭhullaṃ, "
"na accāraddhavīriyaṃ, na atilīnavīriyaṃ, na abhijappā, na nānattasaññā, na "
"atinijjhāyitattaṃ rūpānan’ti. (11)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya27"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.161"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc31"></a>
msgctxt "mn128:27.1"
msgid "So kho ahaṃ, anuruddhā, ‘vicikicchā cittassa upakkileso’ti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn128:27.2"
msgid ""
"iti viditvā vicikicchaṃ cittassa upakkilesaṃ pajahiṃ, ‘amanasikāro cittassa "
